                Contact Us – General Information
                





One Phone Number to Reach both the Money Desk and Customer Service

                        For all Money Desk transactions and customer service needs,  please call 
 1-800-357-3452 and select from the following options:

1 – advances;
2 – advance prepayments, deposits, and wire transactions;
3 – all other needs.                      


The Federal Home Loan Bank 
                        of Boston is located in Boston's Back Bay



