Company Overview of Federal Home Loan Bank of Boston



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Federal Home Loan Bank of Boston develops and delivers financial products and services that support housing finance, community development, and economic growth. The company offers various advances, including overnight advances, short-term fixed-rate advances, fixed-rate putable advances, fixed-rate bullet advances, and variable-rate advances to provide funding alternatives to members in interest-rate environments and situations. It also provides various solutions, such as affordable housing programs, equity builder programs, community development advances, the New England fund, jobs for New England, and helping to house New England for affordable housing or economic development needs of comm...
Federal Home Loan Bank of Boston develops and delivers financial products and services that support housing finance, community development, and economic growth. The company offers various advances, including overnight advances, short-term fixed-rate advances, fixed-rate putable advances, fixed-rate bullet advances, and variable-rate advances to provide funding alternatives to members in interest-rate environments and situations. It also provides various solutions, such as affordable housing programs, equity builder programs, community development advances, the New England fund, jobs for New England, and helping to house New England for affordable housing or economic development needs of communities. In addition, the company offers deposit products comprising demand and overnight deposits, custodial mortgage accounts, and term deposits; financial instruments consisting of standby letters of credit; and mortgage loan financing products. Further, it operates as a correspondent for deposit, funds transfer, and safekeeping services. The company serves savings institutions, commercial banks, credit unions, qualified community development financial institutions, and insurance companies; and housing associates in Connecticut, Maine, Massachusetts, New Hampshire, Rhode Island, and Vermont. Federal Home Loan Bank of Boston was founded in 1932 and is headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts.
